      "content": "it just feels like a loop that never ends. the grief, the tiredness, the feeling that i failed at the one thing i was supposed to do. i look at my life and there's nothing left. i just want to sleep for a long time. like, permanently. i don't even think i want to wake up to another day of this feeling.",
